Go to the documentation of this file.1 /*
2 
3     The ButtonR class creates a rectangle-shaped static-size button, window-resized-not-responsive button.
4 
5     The button size is computed from the font size and length of the text;
6     the text is automatically centered on the button.
7     See mutators to modify the button’s position, the text’s position in the button, and the button’s size.
8 
9     The button's border can be turned on and off.
10     the border's size is computed from the font size and length of the text;
11     modifying the button's size will also modify the border's size.
12 
13     The button's shadow can be turned on and off.
14     The shadow size is computed from the font size and length of the text;
15     modifying the button's size will also modify the shadow's size.
16 
17     The default font is raylib font.
18 
19     Parent class to the ButtonO class
20 
21     Requirement
22     c and c++ 20 or later
23     Raylib library: https://www.raylib.com
24 
25 */
26 
